rry a certain… indulgent edge, and demand serious stamina.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/27819537cac7a2043b4b2d8615801fa6.avif?t=1775896707\" width=1560 height=974 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Core Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Stat Growth × Territory Control</strong>Train to boost your Strength and Agility, take on challenges, defeat rivals, and gradually reclaim territories across the city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/615e97893c637dc99bc3a784b5f58abc.avif?t=1775896707\" width=1560 height=974 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Territory Management × Passive Income</strong>Once a district is secured, collect income and manage operations to steadily grow your underground empire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/4b1cb8e7567cbe26637831b8b24d7a9b.avif?t=1775896707\" width=1560 height=974 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Capital Flow × Loan System</strong>With enough capital, you can offer loans to NPCs, expanding your influence and tightening your control.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/fa06d31b082700ea270e056ca10ae2d7.poster.avif?t=1775896707\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/fa06d31b082700ea270e056ca10ae2d7.webm?t=1775896707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/fa06d31b082700ea270e056ca10ae2d7.mp4?t=1775896707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/bc54dd9db66428e38538c35e8a5aad6a.poster.avif?t=1775896707\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/bc54dd9db66428e38538c35e8a5aad6a.webm?t=1775896707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/bc54dd9db66428e38538c35e8a5aad6a.mp4?t=1775896707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/709d8c0590a199655fbeb069be66f438.poster.avif?t=1775896707\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/709d8c0590a199655fbeb069be66f438.webm?t=1775896707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/709d8c0590a199655fbeb069be66f438.mp4?t=1775896707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Alternative Repayment System</strong>When they can’t pay up—<br>they can always use their body to settle the debt. You know how it works.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of “special tools” and interactions<br>offer layered experiences of control and reward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/6596f4c193d5acdbc6d2a1fda88d169f.avif?t=1775896707\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Now, It’s Your Turn to Take Over</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Territory. Power. Desire.<br>All within your reach.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The only question is—</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Can you handle this life?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>★Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Yesterday, you were just another disposable corporate slave—<br>overworked, underpaid, and eventually thrown out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Today, fate plays a different game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious email from your long-lost uncle hands you everything:<br>his company… and an entire city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete his “objectives,”<br>and a massive inheritance becomes yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But the final line of that message lingers—<br>these tasks won’t just test your mind.<br>They carry a certain… indulgent edge, and demand serious stamina.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/27819537cac7a2043b4b2d8615801fa6.avif?t=1775896707\" width=1560 height=974 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Core Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Stat Growth × Territory Control</strong>Train to boost your Strength and Agility, take on challenges, defeat rivals, and gradually reclaim territories across the city.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/615e97893c637dc99bc3a784b5f58abc.avif?t=1775896707\" width=1560 height=974 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Territory Management × Passive Income</strong>Once a district is secured, collect income and manage operations to steadily grow your underground empire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/4b1cb8e7567cbe26637831b8b24d7a9b.avif?t=1775896707\" width=1560 height=974 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Capital Flow × Loan System</strong>With enough capital, you can offer loans to NPCs, expanding your influence and tightening your control.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/fa06d31b082700ea270e056ca10ae2d7.poster.avif?t=1775896707\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/fa06d31b082700ea270e056ca10ae2d7.webm?t=1775896707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/fa06d31b082700ea270e056ca10ae2d7.mp4?t=1775896707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/bc54dd9db66428e38538c35e8a5aad6a.poster.avif?t=1775896707\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/bc54dd9db66428e38538c35e8a5aad6a.webm?t=1775896707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/bc54dd9db66428e38538c35e8a5aad6a.mp4?t=1775896707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/709d8c0590a199655fbeb069be66f438.poster.avif?t=1775896707\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/709d8c0590a199655fbeb069be66f438.webm?t=1775896707\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/709d8c0590a199655fbeb069be66f438.mp4?t=1775896707\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>• Alternative Repayment System</strong>When they can’t pay up—<br>they can always use their body to settle the debt. You know how it works.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of “special tools” and interactions<br>offer layered experiences of control and reward.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4228690/extras/6596f4c193d5acdbc6d2a1fda88d169f.avif?t=1775896707\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Now, It’s Your Turn to Take Over</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Territory. Power. Desire.<br>All within your reach.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The only question is—</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Can you handle this life?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "short_description": "An adult strategy game set in a modern city. Fired from your job, you’re suddenly tasked by your estranged uncle to reclaim his fallen underworld empire. Build relationships with 13 women, retake territories, expand your power, and rise as the true ruler of Shining Town.", "supported_languages": "English, Japanese, Simplified Chinese, Tradi